Full Body HIIT Band Workout 🏹🏡🏋️‍♀️⠀
⠀
If you are able to get your hands on a resistance band then this is a simple but effective workout that will get your heart rate up, burn calories, and tone 🔥. Anyone can use a resistance band 👦🏻⠀
. ⠀
. ⠀
. ⠀
. ⠀
. ⠀
💕Stay home and #werkitout⠀
💪Like, Share and Save it for later ⠀
.⠀
. ⠀
👉 Follow @werk.itout for more daily inspirations 👈⠀
👉 Follow @werk.itout for more daily inspirations 👈⠀
👉 Follow @werk.itout for more daily inspirations 👈⠀
__________⠀
⠀
4 Rounds of each Set / 30 seconds of each movement / 30 seconds rest at the end of each Set.⠀
•⠀
•⠀
•⠀
Set 1⠀
1️⃣ Lateral Step to Jump ⠀
2️⃣ Push Up to Side Tap⠀
3️⃣ Leg Raise to Sit Up ⠀
⠀
Set 2:⠀
1️⃣ Burpee Plank Jack⠀
2️⃣ Single Arm Row (30sec each side)⠀
3️⃣ Bicycles⠀
⠀
Set 3:⠀
1️⃣ Broad Jump In & Outs ⠀
2️⃣ Front Raise (30sec each side)⠀
3️⃣ Spider Climbers (30sec each side)⠀
